title: Moon Zeit 4/8: Don Trump Jr., Dollywood, The Masters, Grand Prix of Long Beach, See's Candy, Will Smith
itunes:title: Moon Zeit 4/8: Don Trump Jr., Dollywood, The Masters, Grand Prix of Long Beach, See's Candy, Will Smith
description:
In this edition of Moon Zeit, Miles and Jacquis Neal discuss Don Trump Jr's pre-election texts to Mark Meadows, the Right ditching Disney for Dollywood, the Masters Tournament, the Grand Prix of Long Beach, their favorite See's candy, and Will Smith being banned from the Oscars for 10 years.
